data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICE REDUCED FOR A QUICK SALE. SELLER IS MOTIVATED. Welcome to the Spring Lake Reserve Community, an exclusive gated community in the heart of Ocoee, FL. Nestled within this community, you'll discover a charming 2-story home that is sure to captivate you from the moment you arrive. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this spacious home offers over 1800 square feet of comfortable living space. The open kitchen, complete with a kitchen island, seamlessly flows into the dining room and living room on the first floor, creating a perfect space for entertaining and creating lasting memories with loved ones. As you approach the home, you'll notice the rear-facing 2-car garage, providing convenient access and a paver driveway that adds a touch of elegance to your arrival. Step inside and be greeted by an abundance of natural light that pours through the windows, illuminating the home and creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and stunning granite countertops, making it a chef's dream come true. Prepare delicious meals with ease and style, and enjoy the convenience of a kitchen island that offers additional counter space and seating options. Tile flooring throughout the first floor adds a touch of sophistication and is both durable and easy to maintain. An indoor laundry room, complete with a washer and dryer, ensures that your laundry needs are met with utmost convenience. Retreat to the second floor where you'll find the bedrooms, including a master suite that is truly a sanctuary. The master bath features a garden tub, dual sinks, a stand-up shower, and a large walk-in closet, providing ample space and luxury for your personal pampering. One of the highlights of this home is its proximity to to the community pool and playground. Imagine spending lazy summer days by the pool, basking in the sun, or endless hours of play at the nearby playground. This home truly offers the ideal spot within the community. With its prime location in Ocoee, FL, you'll enjoy easy access to local amenities, including schools, shopping centers, dining options, and major roadways. Everything you need is just a short distance away, ensuring a convenient and fulfilling lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to call this exquisite home your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the luxury and comfort of the Spring Lake Reserve Community in Ocoee, FL. We can't wait to welcome you home!
